OL,5,G0150 Couples Come Dine with Me
OL,6,     FThere are silly dances, jokes,
OL,7,     Faccents and plenty of pranks as
OL,8,     Fcouples put their hosting skills
OL,9,     Fto the test in Hertfordshire, in a
OL,10,     Fweek featuring Asian, Anglo-Indian
OL,11,     Fand Irish food.
OL,12,G0245 Free Nelson Mandela
